# PRD drafts — local-only, deleted after `do work` captures them into a UR
docs/prd/*.md
!docs/prd/README.md

# Session records — ephemeral runtime state per actions/session-identity.md
do-work/.sessions/

# Lockfiles — ephemeral runtime state per actions/concurrency-primitives.md
do-work/.locks/

# Capture staging — in-flight UR+REQ drafts; survive crashes, removed on commit/abort
do-work/.capture-staging/

# Cleanup claim sidecars — ephemeral, written by claim_cleanup
do-work/.claims/

# Python bytecode
__pycache__/

# macOS
.DS_Store
